snippet.title: No Man's Sky Endurance Update
snippet.description:
No Man's Sky's 20th free update, Endurance, overhauls the experience of being a freighter captain, with a total rework for space bases that allows players to build visually spectacular structures upon their very own capital ship.

https://www.nomanssky.com/endurance-update
